        "timestamp": "2018-04-03 16:35:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nMost projects do not define a \"docker-pom\" but it is still found in the root of the project. Other projects do explicitly specify \"docker-pom\". \nThere are some repos that do not have a pom.xml but are mostly configuration repos and do not perform any docker push into Nexus3. \n\nAfter this change is merged, I need to move the jobs carefully into these new templates and make sure they work as expected so no corner case is missed.",
